               <p>JOHN SUTCLIFFE. I slept in the same bed with the prisoner - I left him between six and seven o'clock in the morning, and all was correct.</p>
               <p>JOHN WHARTON. These sheets were pawned with me on the 19th of December, by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>ISAAC FULLER. I took the prisoner on the same day, at a coffee-house, and found the duplicate on him.</p>
